Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo Ghoul: re
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tập tiếp theo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:23:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fanculo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhanh lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.27,0:24:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta sẽ không đầu hàng!
